msgid "Secure Infinispan server by default"
msgstr "デフォルトでセキュアなInfinispanサーバ"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:13
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Infinispan server we introduced in 10.0 exposes a single port through "
"which both Hot Rod and HTTP clients can connect."
msgstr "10.0で導入したInfinispanサーバーは、Hot RodとHTTPクライアントの両方が接続できる単一のポートを公開しています。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:15
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While Infinispan has had *very* extensive security support since 7.0, the "
"out-of-the-box default configuration did not enable authentication."
msgstr ""
"Infinispanは7.0から *非常に* 広範なセキュリティサポートを提供してきましたが、デフォルトの設定では認証が有効になりませんでした。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:18
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Infinispan 11.0's server's default configuration, instead, requires "
"authentication.  We have made several improvements to how authentication is "
"configured and the tooling we provide to make the experience as smooth as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Infinispan 11."
"0のサーバーのデフォルト設定では、代わりに認証が必要です。認証の設定方法と提供するツールについて、可能な限りスムーズに体験できるようにいくつかの改善を行いました。"

#. type: Title ==
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:19
#, no-wrap, fuzzy
msgid "Automatic authentication mechanism selection"
msgstr "認証機構の自動選択"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:22
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Previously, when enabling authentication, you had to explicitly define which "
"mechanisms had to be enabled per-protocol, with all of the peculiarities "
"specific to each one (i.e. SASL for Hot Rod, HTTP for REST). Here is an "
"example configuration with Infinispan 10.1 that enables DIGEST "
"authentication:"
msgstr ""
"以前は、認証を有効にする際には、プロトコルごとにどのメカニズムを有効にするかを明示的に定義する必要があり、それぞれに固有の特性がありました (Hot "
"Rod では SASL、REST では HTTP など)。以下に、DIGEST 認証を有効にする Infinispan 10.1 での設定例を示します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:35
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<endpoints socket-binding=\"default\" security-realm=\"default\">\n"
"   <hotrod-connector name=\"hotrod\">\n"
"      <authentication>\n"
"         <sasl mechanisms=\"DIGEST-MD5\" server-name=\"infinispan\"/>\n"
"      </authentication>\n"
"   </hotrod-connector>\n"
"   <rest-connector name=\"rest\">\n"
"      <authentication mechanisms=\"DIGEST\"/>\n"
"   </rest-connector>\n"
"</endpoints>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:38
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In Infinispan 11.0, the mechanisms are automatically selected based on the "
"capabilities of the security realm. Using the following configuration:"
msgstr "Infinispan 11.0 では、セキュリティ領域の機能に基づいてメカニズムが自動的に選択されます。以下の構成を使用します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_posts/2020-06-04-server-secure-by-default.adoc:45
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<endpoints socket-binding=\"default\" security-realm=\"default\">\n"
"   <hotrod-connector name=\"hotrod\" />\n"
"   <rest-connector name=\"rest\"/>\n"
"</endpoints>\n"
msgstr ""

